CULTURAL DATA LICENSE

This license specifically covers all cultural heritage data in this directory including:
- Traditional Indian quotes and sayings (/quotes)
- Festival calendars and cultural celebrations (/festivals)  
- Heritage site information and cultural practices (/heritage)
- Language-specific content and translations (/languages)

You are free to:
- Share — copy and redistribute the material in any medium or format
- Adapt — remix, transform, and build upon the material

Under the following terms:
- Attribution — You must give appropriate credit to DeshChain Foundation
- NonCommercial — You may not use the material for commercial purposes
- ShareAlike — If you remix or build upon the material, you must distribute your contributions under the same license

ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS:
When using cultural data from this collection, you must:
1. Credit "DeshChain Foundation Cultural Heritage Collection"
2. Provide a link to the source repository
3. Specify which cultural elements were used
4. Respect the cultural significance and accuracy of the content

CULTURAL SENSITIVITY:
This collection preserves authentic Indian cultural heritage. Users must:
- Maintain cultural accuracy and respect
- Avoid misrepresentation or distortion
- Consider cultural context in any adaptations
- Acknowledge the traditional sources of this knowledge

For questions about cultural content usage: cultural@deshchain.org